{"tid":380616,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【回應北韓又射導彈】釜山睇六十幾年前解放軍做的好事。","createTime":"2017-08-30T08:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T07:18:57.000Z","uid":37661,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1628e40ba7b851c86db4bb40ea8e1f830cd5df","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"帕卡襲港&mdash;快閃釜山，憑弔聯合國聯軍陣亡士兵。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aymwbqnv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faymwbqnv&h=d058aee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暑假玩快閃，真係自己搵自己笨，早幾個月出晒機票，出發前遇着打風，乜都唔到你控制。<br />\n<br />\n星期六零晨機去，星期日晏晝返，完全無Buffer 位，仲要分咗兩間航空公司去程回程，想改都無得改。<br />\n<br />\n去程釜山航空零晨機出發，2點幾飛，到達釜山朝早六點幾，回程唔想太夜所以要坐UO，唔想星期日夜晚12點先到香港，港豬第日都仲要返工呀。<br />\n<br />\n韓戰時間表<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/68ncfz9i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F68ncfz9i&h=2d18890d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98f1f2b79127f9ade0468c215e168048b4c9ac34","tid":380616,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"811125f71798db0775f219f32f0c7ee2b8f28534","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"釜山航空，網上可以 Check-in 揀位，但好似無得網上印登機證，一定要去到機場 counter 報到先印俾你。<br />\n<br />\n2點05分機，十一點九已經咁多人排隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/64enjtx5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F64enjtx5&h=37962868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對釜山航空係無乜期望，但佢就可以包件20kg 寄倉行李，不過我回程坐唔 UO 就唔帶行李了。<br />\n<br />\n釜山航空架空中巴士A321，座位跟前排距離非常闊，坐大機 777 都未必有咁既距離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0ua3b6nr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0ua3b6nr&h=a588de08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過飛機餐只有蛋糕一個同飲品，個蛋糕仲要係好齋乜都無果啲。<br />\n<br />\n飛到釜山天光啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hl91gsya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhl91gsya&h=aa20abc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過到釜山都係朝早六點八左右，我就乜都唔急，佢 De唔Delay都無所謂，反正咁早都係要搵地方食嘢先。<br />\n<br />\n入去入境大堂，見到前面好多人排隊，咁諗着跟埋排就無衰，但見佢哋個個都拎着張橙色既健康申報表，但我又無，我就離開條隊去搵。<br />\n<br />\n跟着見到有職員叫 Hong Kong Passport 行另一條通道過，原來我哋係唔洗填果份嘢，到我再行條通道去到排入境隊就變咗排後咗。<br />\n<br />\n過 Passport Control 只需要打手指，呢次唔洗影相，上次去濟洲明明有架喎，我見前面果個都有，係我唔洗，我仲喺度等影相，佢就同我講 Finish。"},{"pid":"0f73078eecbe11caa0ef2e93aaa29ae410c610c0","tid":380616,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1f0994dd27289c1c5a77bba3bef6781019c87307","tid":380616,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8031fab8ac04333ef8d638427a445a9ced704e60","tid":380616,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"早兩個禮拜都係快閃首爾, 入境都要影相"},{"pid":"3b8a4bd7a5b73cc2269e51822b5203bf4f2f9892","tid":380616,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"跟住呢"},{"pid":"9c411e9483df8298ba36399457a59a0773597169","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟住呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住咪今日繼續囉。<br />\n<br />\n私人嘢梗係返工先做架啦。"},{"pid":"b5bc7e0f0ffffc941aa5e6beca837eae037eea3f","tid":380616,"uid":117048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:42:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94f0559a3fcb59a6ed2e47e2e2babd8fd62d06ac","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"由於大把時間關係，之前睇過資料話韓國機場可以申請E-道 (韓國同香港互相開放E-道俾彼此既國民用)，咁就喺機場亂咁兜，諗着搵果個申請E-道既地方，結果係搵唔到，原來係要入咗禁區先有。<br />\n<br />\n唯有離開機場出市區，在濟洲買的T-Money 卡，在釜山都用到，但機場間7仔就話唔做增值，叫我去車站做。<br />\n<br />\n機場對外交通有紫色線的架空單軌列車，仲有幾條市內巴士 (好似去好近既地方)，另外仲有兩條超貴既機場豪華巴士線去釜山火車站 (南浦洞) 同埋海雲台，不過就要成6-7000 Won。<br />\n<br />\n自己坐紫色線架空單軌列車出去附近市區轉巴士落番南浦洞都唔洗2000Won，車程都唔洗1個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n架空單軌車站，喺國內線大樓對開，國際線大樓要行1-2百米過去。車站有自助售票機或T-Money 增值機，當然去韓國點都要買張T-Money 卡，轉幾次車就幫你慳番張卡錢。<br />\n<br />\n架空列車呢程好似1300 Won，咁你出面再轉巴士或地鐵就可能再扣幾百Won，否則你就要俾多千幾won轉車。<br />\n<br />\n無乜人坐的單軌車<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/63rb4tqo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F63rb4tqo&h=900e16bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6d50322e77703d3bb87682c746c103b5e548a5f","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:18:00.000Z","msg":"釜山第一站要去西面果邊醫肚，架空單軌列車坐3個站到沙上站，再轉地鐵過去西面。<br />\n<br />\n網上搵咗街話出名既海鮮鍋&mdash;海東海鮮鍋，喺樂天酒店附近，啲人講到好似好抵食又好食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rq3eivsd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frq3eivsd&h=0df7480b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到都係八點左右，已經開咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qnci19dk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqnci19dk&h=03dae4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係啲最唔想食既小碟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5uf1d038\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5uf1d038&h=73387dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫咗個小既海鮮鍋 (35000 Won)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b0q6m3rd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb0q6m3rd&h=6f0ea986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鮑魚同八爪魚都係仲郁梗果陣擺落去，你喺個煲蓋會見到佢地喺度狂郁。<br />\n<br />\n間鋪個阿豬媽會幫你剪碎啲鮑魚、八爪魚、隻蟹都同你剪開一件件，去埋鰓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ya1vbnid\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fya1vbnid&h=12680bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過呢個海鮮湯就好一般，同埋佢係唔會跟個飯俾你，覺得味道仲衰過我在濟山食果個15000won 鮑魚海鮮鍋。"},{"pid":"7eb8757216c9fa885d1bfc5c7213cacfefd126c0","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"西面附近有個釜田市場，由樂天附近的地下街經過地鐵站可以穿到過去附近。<br />\n<br />\n港女在韓國應該好受歡迎，西面都有市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rpki0qbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frpki0qbg&h=986d5814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n釜田市場好似蜘蛛網咁，四通八達，但係啲攤檔安排勁亂，唔會分類集中某條巷，呢檔賣海鮮，隔離又賣菜，啲生熟食物都係黐着賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fh1wo0ul\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffh1wo0ul&h=282e4ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能係水蜜桃季節，度度都見到水蜜桃賣，拳頭咁大隻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xbtws30e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxbtws30e&h=9c786f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附近的一間教堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o3riwvht\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo3riwvht&h=1c5402ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15591a0b9b404a627b74b28344141c8510a2e0a9","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"下一站，呢個快閃唯一一個景點&mdash;韓國聯合國紀念公園<br />\n<br />\nUnited Nations Memorial Cemetery In Korea<br />\n<br />\n參與韓戰的聯合國軍隊包括16個國家，5個醫療輔助國，韓戰陣亡的聯合國士兵為40,896人，而美國人佔了最大部份為36,492人，此處安葬了部份陣亡的聯合國士兵，總數為2300個。<br />\n<br />\n紀念公園年中無休，每天上午10點都會有升旗儀式，降旗儀式就分冬夏季，夏季為下午5點，冬季為4點。<br />\n<br />\n公園外<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0a6ml4b3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0a6ml4b3&h=26fd3ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n悼念館<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l802y6ij\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl802y6ij&h=57bf2304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n悼念館會有韓戰歷史的影片播放，韓語旁白，字幕就隨你要求，會有職員問你國籍，然後播放你國家的語文字幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v07ocd6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv07ocd6r&h=0f753977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好簡單介紹韓戰歷史，由北韓南下攻打南韓到聯合國派兵把北韓打到去近鴨綠江，之後支共介入派兵把聯合國軍隊打到38線附近對峙，到簽訂和約，及此公墓的歷史，有參與戰事仍在世的老兵訪問，亦有講述一個陣亡的軍人的太太，在百年歸老後，選擇把自己安葬在丈夫的墓穴旁。"},{"pid":"042ae9fbe7fc5b17157abca45b87db9adbc2d808","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"另一個紀念館<br />\n<br />\n展示了不少分散世界各地及在韓國有關韓戰的紀念碑相片，聯合國聯軍相片及各種紀念物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y0tmh7x3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy0tmh7x3&h=75c102dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0pmtevwi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0pmtevwi&h=a6da3c23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nb1quc7v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnb1quc7v&h=178337b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iqpnf6su\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiqpnf6su&h=2be0626f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7nhfxtbu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7nhfxtbu&h=3b814732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去完悼念館及紀念館，你會更加痛恨支那共產黨的所作所為。"},{"pid":"edd49ab416bf25442441e99457690224b0ddbbad","tid":380616,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"各參與國陣亡軍人墓碑及紀念碑<br />\n<br />\n國旗區<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gx2u1mdb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgx2u1mdb&h=cb036fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土耳其的紀念碑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ump6xv29\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fump6xv29&h=b8b5c6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6y1s84ex\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6y1s84ex&h=deceb1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土耳其軍人墓園區<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/43qoci0s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F43qoci0s&h=4c8cd9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國的紀念碑<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jeyqu86z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjeyqu86z&h=3133906c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓的紀念碑<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wyevjkb9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwyevjkb9&h=764cc81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭的紀念碑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ftphi1jw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fftphi1jw&h=b4ea2943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d864b82e30c98d4c7c60d73660798f4aeddc6ef","tid":380616,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"咁高質都冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e14a45eb915d707f171d56a9d3ea2028968afd","tid":380616,"uid":51036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"師兄等待中"}]}